a:50:{i:1241267;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241267";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10607";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Arcadia";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"769";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:149:"&quot;If that were the case, why would you be here? Maya is painfully thorough. I doubt she&#039;d let someone in that ended up being a threat.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423103602";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#1befe0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231036011";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f30af3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241270;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241270";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Glance";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1251";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:531:"&quot;And if circumstances changed? What if I left? What if I was consumed by twilight? What if Zalan or Maya decided...&quot; Glance pauses for a minute, aheming, as she puts on her best gruff and tough voice, &quot; &#039;Gee, I really hate that Glance kid today, Maya. Me too Zalan, we should kick her out and then put a bounty on her head for sport.&#039; &quot; She stops. Honestly the voice just sounds adorable coming out of Glance than anything else - Like a small kid in school trying to intimidate everyone with big talk.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423103912";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#0abb87";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231039110";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b92dea";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241273;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241273";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10607";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Arcadia";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"769";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:209:"/me frowns. &quot;Zalan and Maya hardly seem like the type to do something like that. Leaving is your choice, but for Twilight, well...that is what I&#039;m here to research, so I&#039;d try to save you.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423104383";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#1befe0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231043812";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f30af3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241275;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241275";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Glance";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1251";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:100:"Glance circles Arcadia once, before responding, &quot;Well, it pays to have contingency plans.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423104590";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#0abb87";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231045916";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b92dea";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241276;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241276";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10607";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Arcadia";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"769";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:111:"&quot;I like to go with the flow. Preparation comes from honing my abilities and broadening my knowledge.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423104851";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#1befe0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231048491";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f30af3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241283;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241283";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Glance";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1251";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:130:"&quot;All rivers flow into the ocean eventually. Do you want to end up in Finrest?&quot; Glance giggles at her rather odd insight.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423105104";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#0abb87";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231051049";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b92dea";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241286;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241286";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10607";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Arcadia";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"769";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:107:"&quot;I&#039;d rather end up in Baribria, their libraries are unlike any other,&quot; she comments happily.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423105146";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#1befe0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231051449";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f30af3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241292;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241292";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Glance";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1251";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:167:"&quot;Aha, then you will want to go where the flow does not!&quot; Glance replies. &quot;Baribria is pretty cool. Well, not cool. It&#039;s warm. Hot, sometimes.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423105303";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#0abb87";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231053023";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b92dea";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241303;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241303";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10607";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Arcadia";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"769";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:187:"&quot;My blood is rather mellow. I&#039;d be fine no matter what temperature it generally was. And I tend to not go with the flow, it&#039;s been like that my whole life.&quot; She states";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423105555";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#1befe0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231055527";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f30af3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241306;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241306";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Glance";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1251";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:105:"&quot;So...Do you want to go with the flow, or against it? Your words are confusing!&quot; Glance flails.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423105665";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#0abb87";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231056668";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b92dea";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241315;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241315";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10607";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Arcadia";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"769";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:110:"&quot;Neither,&quot; she says simply. &quot;I go my own way. I make my own flow so to speak,&quot; she shrugs.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423106087";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#1befe0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231060854";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f30af3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241317;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241317";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Glance";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1251";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:252:"Glance stands there. Parsing. Eventually... &quot;NOPE!&quot; Glance shouts, throwing her two forehooves up in the air, one still coated in glass. &quot;I quit!&quot; She annouces, planting her hooves back on the ground, turning and beginning to leave.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423106302";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#0abb87";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231063036";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b92dea";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241320;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241320";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10607";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Arcadia";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"769";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:128:"/me blinks, then slithers up to Glance and tries to stop her. &quot;What are you talking about? What do you mean you quit?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423106367";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#1befe0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231063657";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f30af3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241322;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241322";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Glance";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1251";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:152:"Glance keeps on walking, though she responds to Arcadia. &quot;I&#039;m done! Your logic, I give up!&quot; She responds, in a raised, exaggerated voice.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423106465";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#0abb87";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231064665";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b92dea";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241327;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241327";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10607";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Arcadia";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"769";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:158:"/me slithers in front of Glance, hooves on her hips. &quot;MY logic? Yours is worse! You won&#039;t even tell me what you do! I told you AND showed you!&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423106551";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#1befe0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231065495";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f30af3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241330;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241330";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Glance";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1251";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:345:"Glance walks into Arcadia, trying to walk through Arcadia as punishment for blocking her path. &quot;That isn&#039;t a question of logic! I already told you why I wouldn&#039;t, but your logic is: &#039;I go with the flow, I don&#039;t go with the flow, I ignore the flow and subtitute my own&#039;! Those are three conflicting statements!&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423106691";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#0abb87";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231066917";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b92dea";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241334;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241334";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10607";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Arcadia";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"769";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:225:"/me pushes her back and holds her in place. &quot;Then Ill clarify what I meant right now. For me there is no flow. I follow my own ambitions. Sometimes they go with the flow, sometimes they dont. It&#039;s that simple.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423106869";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#1befe0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231068676";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f30af3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241335;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241335";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Glance";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1251";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:171:"Glance begins to seriously push back against Arcadia. The little pony is actually stronger than she looks, and her single glass-coated hoof would be hard to get a grip on.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423107093";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#0abb87";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231070946";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b92dea";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241351;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241351";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10607";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Arcadia";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"769";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:86:"/me removes her hold. &quot;Act your age, not your size. How old are you anyway?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423108250";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#1befe0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231082482";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f30af3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241352;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241352";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Glance";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1251";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:166:"Glance keeps on walking, assuming Arcadia is no longer in her way. Otherwise she just walks into Arcadia&#039;s belly/underside. &quot;Old enough.&quot; She responds.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423108307";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#0abb87";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231083084";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b92dea";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241354;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241354";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10607";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Arcadia";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"769";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:72:"&quot;Would you stop just walking into me? What&#039;s your issue?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423108341";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#1befe0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231083394";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f30af3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241358;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241358";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Glance";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1251";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:71:"&quot;As I recall, YOU moved into MY way.&quot; Glance accuses Arcadia.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423108383";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#0abb87";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231083841";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b92dea";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241359;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241359";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10607";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Arcadia";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"769";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:116:"&quot;Because you just started walking away in the middle of our conversation! We were getting along fine too!&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423108425";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#1befe0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231084236";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f30af3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241363;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241363";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Glance";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1251";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:83:"&quot;I did say I was done, too.&quot; Glance keeps trying to walk through Arcadia.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423108574";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#0abb87";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231085747";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b92dea";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241365;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241365";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10607";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Arcadia";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"769";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:215:"/me is a heavy snakebutt, and doesn&#039;t budge. &quot;What is your issue anyway? First you cut yourself, then refuse to tell me what you can do or what that glass is for, and now you are trying to storm off.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423108640";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#1befe0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231086386";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f30af3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241366;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241366";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Glance";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1251";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:196:"&quot;Number one, that was for science. Number two, showing is better than telling, Number three, I&#039;m a free pony! I can leave whenever I want.&quot; Glance keeps up the walking into Arcadia.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423108781";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#0abb87";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231087828";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b92dea";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241378;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241378";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10607";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Arcadia";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"769";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:96:"She pauses for a minute. Maybe try a different approach? &quot;Is something bothering you?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423110319";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#1befe0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231103170";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f30af3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241382;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241382";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Glance";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1251";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:136:"&quot;Yep! You&#039;re in my way.&quot; Glance replies. &quot;But other than that, no. Mostly I want to spend some time to myself.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423110595";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#0abb87";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231105960";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b92dea";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241408;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241408";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10607";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Arcadia";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"769";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:25:"(( Sorry for the wait. ))";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423113051";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#1befe0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231130473";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f30af3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241410;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241410";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10607";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Arcadia";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"769";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:93:"&quot;Well...If you say so. Maybe we can talk again soon on better terms huh?&quot; She asks.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423113071";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#1befe0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231130681";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f30af3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241411;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241411";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Glance";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1251";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:125:"&quot;Sure.&quot; Glance replies. &quot;I hope this means you will get out of my way, before I start applying the horn.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423113172";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#0abb87";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231131736";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b92dea";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241422;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241422";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10607";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Arcadia";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"769";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:58:"/me slithers aside and gestures forward with a little bow.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423113408";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#1befe0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231134045";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f30af3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241425;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241425";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Glance";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1251";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:110:"Glance, unhindered, immediately moves forward, as she has of course been walking into Arcadia the entire time.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423113450";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#0abb87";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231134515";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b92dea";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241442;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241442";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10607";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Arcadia";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"769";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:12:"(( Scene? ))";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423114284";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#1befe0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231142825";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f30af3";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1241443;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1241443";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Glance";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1251";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:8:"((Yes.))";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423114298";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#0abb87";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14231142989";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b92dea";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1248815;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1248815";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Jackle";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"445";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:556:"The masked meditator opens her eyes in response to being addressed directly, turning her head to face Creo. She usually meditates to pass the time, often passengers don&#039;t particularly talk to their neighbor. Talking was far less boring than meditation however, so perhaps this fleeting, initial small-talk comment could blossom into something larger. Maybe. The masked pony hasn&#039;t quite gone so far as to fully upheave her position and lean back in the chair with hooves outstretched. &quot;Thanks. Stressed?&quot; The pony questions the griffon.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423483686";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f54500";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14234836871";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1248817;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1248817";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11722";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Creo_Unguis";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1249";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:369:"&quot;I suppose you could say that. Just... new to. Everything.&quot; Of course, Creo in her infinate niavity could never comprehend how idiotic that may sound to one who was born in this land, but still what was said, was said, and Creo was left, sighing and sitting back. Flumping essentially into the back of the seats. Who knew what this comment may lead to though?";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423483803";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#316b81";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14234837976";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#0b96c1";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1248822;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1248822";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Jackle";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"445";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:348:"Jackle eyes Creo over carefully for a second, namely locking onto the satchel Creo has. &quot;Come from the lake, have you?&quot; Jackle comments. &quot;I&#039;m a laker myself.&quot; Jackle attempts to provide whatever immediate comfort she could to Creo, common ground in misfortune and/or tragedy might open up Creo a little bit more, hopefully.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423484232";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f54500";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14234842328";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1248830;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1248830";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11722";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Creo_Unguis";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1249";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:433:"/me drooped nigh immediately, &quot;Yes, from the lake. And now, the part of figuring out where to go...&quot; Another sigh, as Creo looked about those on the train, &quot;You&#039;re a laker too? How... did you ever decide how to start off your life? Your new one. Hay, there are weapons here I&#039;ve never seen before, new buildings, new.... ponies... sorta. Snake things, ponies floating swords about, and what? On trains.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423484728";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#316b81";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14234847227";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#0b96c1";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1248831;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1248831";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Jackle";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"445";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:411:"Jackle chuckles a little. &quot;Admittingly, where I came from was a more advanced place than here. That isn&#039;t to say Unrest isn&#039;t advanced, mind you. As for my life? It sort of just fell into place.&quot; Jackle keeps everything vague, not one to ramble on about specifics unless they&#039;re requested. She now decides to lean back into the chair, relaxing herself, settling in for the conversation.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423485195";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f54500";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14234851956";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1248832;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1248832";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11722";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Creo_Unguis";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1249";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:344:"&quot;Well now&#039;s a good time for life to fall before me and throw me some miraculous map. Where did you get the sword, anyway?&quot; Creo flicking quickly to a better subject, feeling welling memories, emotions again getting to her. Perhaps breaking down was exactly what she needed, but that would not be easy. Public stole that from her.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423485338";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#316b81";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14234853327";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#0b96c1";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1248841;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1248841";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Jackle";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"445";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:242:"&quot;From before Unrest, actually. Gift from my father, also the reason why everything fell into place.&quot; Jackle again, sticking to only broad strokes with her responses. &quot;Where are you from? Why the Bastion?&quot; Jackle questions.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423485764";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f54500";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14234857551";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1248844;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1248844";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11722";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Creo_Unguis";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1249";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:397:"&quot;Equestria... hard to explain the place to someone who was not there before. I suppose.&quot; Unless the other was indeed from Equestria, more outland areas, away from the calmer centers, &quot;But... the Bastion of Life. Well I don&#039;t know. May as well visit it, and the City of Yesterday... or whatever it was called. Get some idea of where I&#039;m going to throw my stones with.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423486059";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#316b81";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14234860540";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#0b96c1";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1248850;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1248850";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Jackle";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"445";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:506:"&quot;I know of Equestria. It was sort of my first life.&quot; Jackle explains. &quot;With my life before Unrest being my second.&quot; She clarifies. &quot;What part of Equestria were you from? If you&#039;re looking for something similiar to the out of city life, Bastion has that covered pretty well. &#039;Course, you could always stay at one of the smaller towns on the rail line as well. The big providences aren&#039;t the only option. Real question is what are you, most ideally, looking for?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423486331";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f54500";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14234863314";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1248868;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1248868";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11722";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Creo_Unguis";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1249";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:422:"&quot;A horseshoe on a hook. I don&#039;t know what I am looking for. I&#039;m looking for home, or something I can make for it. As for what part? The gryphon places, the pony places... I travelled more than I stayed. More Ponyville, and home.&quot; She frowned, &quot;But the Bastion sounds like the safest place to make up my mind, considering they essentially booted me from... whatever that place back there was.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423486676";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#316b81";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14234866710";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#0b96c1";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1248889;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1248889";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Jackle";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"445";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:371:"&quot;Yeah...It&#039;s a joint effort between the four major cities. It is a city in it&#039;s own right culturally, though you need to be a citizen of one of the other cities to live there. It&#039;s a pretty cool place to live, actually.&quot; Jackle explains. &quot;By the way, I&#039;m Jackle.&quot; Jackle extends her right hoof to Creo, veiled by her kimono sleeve.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423487005";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f54500";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14234870052";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1248905;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1248905";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11722";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Creo_Unguis";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1249";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:301:"&quot;Not the first time I&#039;ve been told that.&quot; Creo shrugging, and nodding at the other&#039;s introduction, &quot;Pleasure meeting. I suppose. I&#039;m Creo.&quot; The gryphon bumping the hoof with a snorted giggle. Gryphon-pony relations were always silly at points of hoofshakes and paws.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423487477";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#316b81";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14234874721";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#0b96c1";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1248917;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1248917";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Jackle";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"445";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:455:"That was certainly unexpected. Jackle withdraws the hoof, still satisfied by the interaction however. &quot;Yeah...The sentinels aren&#039;t all that helpful. Their job is a little stressful, they kind of have to push people out the door quickly incase something horrible drops through, but I didn&#039;t exactly have a positive time again. Then again...&quot; Jackle pauses to chuckle lightly. &quot;I did attack them. Fair&#039;s fair on that one.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423487842";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f54500";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14234878418";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1248920;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1248920";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"11722";s:6:"handle";s:11:"Creo_Unguis";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1249";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:269:"/me could only snort at that! &quot;You? And I take it you... won? Sort of? Or they end up knocking you sleepylike?&quot; Creo giving a fading grin, as she flicked her eyes to the sword. No doubt that thing could make a real mess of someone&#039;s day. Poor sentinels. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423488010";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#316b81";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14234880045";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#0b96c1";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1248924;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1248924";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"17";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"47";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Jackle";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"445";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";N;s:4:"text";s:389:"&quot;Not even close.&quot; Jackle chuckles. &quot;I&#039;m actually kind of lucky their shots only incapacitated me, or that I didn&#039;t wound any of them. Sentinels don&#039;t bother containing anything that manages to hurt them. Starting off in water is a pretty huge disadvantage, by the way. Plus there&#039;s like...Thirty of them in that place, not that I cared at the time.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1423488305";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f54500";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14234883054";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffffff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"1";s:6:"viewed";N;}}